description: Zodiac Flea & Tick Control Spot On for Dogs is a long-lasting topical treatment designed to keep your pet protected from fleas and ticks for up to 30 days. It kills and repels fleas, flea eggs, flea larvae, and Brown Dog ticks. It kills fleas and tick through contact. The unique applicator design helps prevent misapplication and package contains a 4-month supply.
